      "content": "that's a great start, really captures the atmosphere. to make it even more immersive, i want to start introducing the people who inhabit the area. can you describe a few different types of characters the protagonist might run into on these streets? i want them to feel authentic to a neighborhood that's struggling—maybe some guys hanging out on the corner or people just passing through that make the protagonist feel like they don't belong. give me some specific details on how they look and act so i can get a sense of the vibe.",
